::KitKat::

She looked up as she heard Darkmouse say there was an intruder. She 
wiped her face and opened her link. "Drillbit, War, we have an 
intruder. Lock onto him and take him prisoner. I want no mech fluid 
shed if it can be helped."

She lowered her head and sighed heavily. She couldn't believe what 
was happening. She noticed that she had little time left untill she 
had to go and meet Megatron. She wasn't really sure as to what to do. 
But she hoped that the Matrix would show her the way.
